that at least shows it:
http://www.engadget.com/2007/06/06/hitachis-external-easy-hard-drive-...

Unfortunately, it came formatted FAT32...which for a 1-terabyte HDD seems
absurd to say the least.  In any event, I reformatted it (converted it,
actually) to NTFS, and use it as my backup destination for my automatic MS
